item.description:
Tickets are sold out!

We have a small block of Bleacher tickets for the 4:10pm Nationally Televised Red Sox Yankees Game on Saturday, August 6.

We will probably be going out before and after the game so please E Mail me if you already have tickets and will be attending on your own.

Additional tickets may become available so add your name to the waiting list if you have the cash. No picture on the site, no ticket.

This should be one of the better games and series of the year.
item.name: Red Sox vs New York Yankees Game Tickets in the Bleachers
